reviewText: If your child is a Bratz fanatic this is for you. My niece loves every Bratz product that's on the market. I heard they aren't selling anymore of these in the stores so this was an e cel lent buy online.

This adorable DVD movie is perfect for little girls around 3-10 years old. In fact most people of any age would like this movie. It's very cute and it has a good story. All the little girls in my family (3 altogether) just love all Bratz movies and cartoons. For less than $5 and only 3 days to deliver, the little ones smiles and laughter made this a true bargain. Although I haven't seen it in stores, I bet it would cost several dollars more. If you have little girls who haven't seen this I recommend turning them on to it. Don't be surprised if some of the adults (like me) start enjoying it as well.
It's awesome and tons of fun but my cover is not like that cover they show but I still love it anyway!
